sentence: Minnim nea Kwasi nim, nanso Kwasi nim nea minim.
Dɛn na Bible ka wɔ ho?
• Ma wo yere nhu sɛ wopene nufuma so.
Ɛkaa abɔde ho nsɛm pii a ɛma yenya Yehowa dɔ ho anisɔ kɛse.
Ɛyɛɛ no nwonwa ma obisaa me sɛ
Sɛnea Asamoah gye di sɛ biribiara wɔ ne bere ne baabi.
Mekyerɛkyerɛɛ mu sɛ Yehowa Adansefo nso hyɛ eyi ho nkuran.
Bere a midii awia aduan wiei no, mesan kɔɔ adwumayɛbea hɔ.
